ceably slowed down. My hair feels stronger and looks thicker at the roots. Highly recommend.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2FjOwWWOe_text","label":"gg2FjOwWWOe_text","default":"<p>Alyssa M , Phoenix AZ</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggl4Q0bGxe2_text","label":"ggl4Q0bGxe2_text","default":"<p>My hair was dry, dull, and breaking constantly. This shampoo brought back softness and shine. It actually feels nourished instead of stripped. I’m obsessed.<br><br>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzquEtSZcR_text","label":"ggzquEtSZcR_text","default":"<p>Emily Johnson</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtu7vVG4oo_text","label":"ggtu7vVG4oo_text","default":"<p>“I noticed a visible reduction in hair fall after just a few washes. My hair feels stronger and healthier.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6ZaMc7hpv_text","label":"gg6ZaMc7hpv_text","default":"<p>Michael Anderson</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkWmFcifj4_text","label":"ggkWmFcifj4_text","default":"<p>I was dealing with thinning hair, and this shampoo has definitely helped improve volume and texture.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggX39z8TJSd_text","label":"ggX39z8TJSd_text","default":"<p>Olivia Brown</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1Cnp80FuK_text","label":"gg1Cnp80FuK_text","default":"<p>love that it uses natural ingredients. My hair looks shinier and more manageable now.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNFc4VHrD9_text","label":"ggNFc4VHrD9_text","default":"<p>Daniel Roberts</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggttphkRBfX_text","label":"ggttphkRBfX_text","default":"<p>My hair feels much smoother and less prone to breakage since I started using this.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8WXeI_yKb_text","label":"gg8WXeI_yKb_text","default":"<p>Rachel P , Columbus OH</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJpm_b1e7Z_text","label":"ggJpm_b1e7Z_text","default":"<p>It’s rare to find a natural product that delivers results. The rosemary scent is clean and spa-like, and my hair feels stronger with every wash.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"}],
